998
01:11:39,993 --> 01:11:42,755
You have to actually engage with them as it's happening.

999
01:11:43,255 --> 01:11:45,576
So it's very, the enforcement is the most challenging part.

1000
01:11:46,116 --> 01:11:49,819
And we don't want to necessarily put our orders for the sake of putting out orders.

1001
01:11:50,279 --> 01:11:58,605
We'd rather put out guidance, focus on education, tell folks that this is in their best interest instead of mandating orders that we can't necessarily enforce.

1002
01:11:58,685 --> 01:12:04,149
So our focus, and just like Councilor Scarpelli said, a huge focus on education.

